item.title: whonix-packages-dependencies 3.4.2-1 is outdated
item.dc:creator: 0brand
item.description:
Hi ef86

Whonix 13 is no longer available for download and support questions are no longer accepted. You should either:

1. Download new Whonix 14 Templates (recommended). https://whonix.org/wiki/Upgrading_Whonix_13_to_Whonix_14#Download_New_Templates

2. Upgrade your Whonix 13 Templates in place.

https://whonix.org/wiki/Upgrading_Whonix_13_to_Whonix_14
